---
// SecretsRotation.astro — Secret rotation flow
---
<div class="sr-wrap">
  <h3 class="sr-title">Rotation — The Forgotten Step</h3>
  <p class="sr-sub">A secret that never changes is a secret waiting to be exploited. Rotation limits blast radius.</p>
  <div class="sr-flow">
    <div class="sr-step sr-s1"><span class="sr-n">1</span><div class="sr-info"><span class="sr-nm">Generate new secret</span><span class="sr-d">Vault/SM creates a new credential pair</span></div></div>
    <div class="sr-arrow">↓</div>
    <div class="sr-step sr-s2"><span class="sr-n">2</span><div class="sr-info"><span class="sr-nm">Update target system</span><span class="sr-d">New password set on database/service</span></div></div>
    <div class="sr-arrow">↓</div>
    <div class="sr-step sr-s3"><span class="sr-n">3</span><div class="sr-info"><span class="sr-nm">Dual-active window</span><span class="sr-d">Both old and new work for grace period (rolling deploy)</span></div></div>
    <div class="sr-arrow">↓</div>
    <div class="sr-step sr-s4"><span class="sr-n">4</span><div class="sr-info"><span class="sr-nm">Revoke old secret</span><span class="sr-d">Old credential invalidated after all consumers updated</span></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="sr-freq">
    <span class="sr-ft">Recommended rotation frequency:</span>
    <div class="sr-freqs">
      <span class="sr-fi"><strong>API keys:</strong> 90 days</span>
      <span class="sr-fi"><strong>DB passwords:</strong> 30 days (or use dynamic per-request)</span>
      <span class="sr-fi"><strong>TLS certs:</strong> Auto via ACME/cert-manager</span>
      <span class="sr-fi"><strong>After incident:</strong> Immediately, all secrets potentially exposed</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .sr-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .sr-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 .25rem}.sr-sub{color:#64748b;font-size:.78rem;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .sr-flow{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:0;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
  .sr-step{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 16px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;border:1px solid #334155;width:100%;max-width:380px;opacity:0;animation:srIn .4s ease forwards}
  .sr-s1{animation-delay:.1s}.sr-s2{animation-delay:.3s}.sr-s3{animation-delay:.5s}.sr-s4{animation-delay:.7s}
  @keyframes srIn{to{opacity:1}}
  .sr-n{font-family:monospace;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:800;width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(74,222,128,.1);color:#4ade80;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0}
  .sr-info{flex:1}.sr-nm{display:block;color:#e2e8f0;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700}.sr-d{display:block;color:#94a3b8;font-size:.67rem;margin-top:1px}
  .sr-arrow{color:#475569;font-size:.7rem;height:12px;display:flex;align-items:center}
  .sr-freq{background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:10px;padding:12px 14px;border:1px solid #334155}
  .sr-ft{color:#f59e0b;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;display:block;margin-bottom:6px}
  .sr-freqs{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px}
  .sr-fi{color:#94a3b8;font-size:.68rem}.sr-fi strong{color:#e2e8f0}
</style>
